This is task for a job interview at Inter System

1. Create OOP based class to calculate taxes in given countries.
2. Connect to test database and perform given queries.


Realisation:
Whole task is set up for easy recreation using docker in a way that can be used in DEV.
HOW TO RUN IT?
1. Download repo
2. Navigate to main directory
3. Run docker compose up -d
  This will build php image, install composer and required PHPUnit.
  (PHPUnit should not be present in production!!!)
4. You can now go into container shell via 
  docker exec -it contaner_name /bin/bash
5. Now navigate into /var/www/html and execute ./vendor/bin/phpunit to run tests
